comments[19]{created_at,author,text}:
  "2026-06-10T10:33:45.487Z",codex-impl,"Mutation-surface specialist read-only pass: pm-xnkd close --duplicate-of, pm-p9hw create --parent fail-fast/default escape hatch, and pm-esf6 root --id-only are not implemented in current branch. close.ts/register-mutation.ts have no duplicateOf/--duplicate-of path; create.ts still uses settings.validation.parent_reference with default governance parent_reference=warn and tests assert warning behavior; global contracts/main/MCP/completions expose --no-changed-fields/fullChangedFields only, no --id-only. Expected follow-up surfaces: src/cli/commands/close.ts, src/cli/register-mutation.ts, src/cli/commands/create.ts, src/core/item/parent-reference-policy.ts, src/core/shared/constants.ts, src/cli/main.ts, src/sdk/cli-contracts.ts, src/mcp/server.ts, src/cli/commands/completion.ts, tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json, docs/COMMANDS.md, docs/AGENT_GUIDE.md, and focused unit/integration/MCP regressions."
  "2026-06-10T10:33:54.434Z",codex-impl,"Read-surface inspection: pm-awfr is implemented via DEFAULT_COMPACT_LIST_FIELDS including parent and has unit coverage. pm-ojpq is only partially present: hierarchy/progress completion-style stats exist, but high_level entries lack children_total/children_closed/completion_pct and recently_created/unparented sections are absent from section types, defaults, builders, and renderers. pm-eaer is not implemented: aggregate has no --completion option, no completion counters/pct fields, no registration/contracts/completion/docs/tests. No files edited by specialist."
  "2026-06-10T10:35:03.757Z",codex-impl,"Linked-test specialist read-only pass: pm-vcr2/GH-191 and GH-193 are partially implemented via --add-json parser/wiring, but the GH-191 two-token --add command UX/guidance is not implemented. pm-p86h/GH-194 selectors are partially implemented via src/core/test/run-selectors.ts and runTest selection metadata. Specialist tsc check failed at src/cli/commands/test.ts optional linkedTest.command passed to string-only safety helpers. Remaining gaps noted: selector/add-json tests, background arg propagation for selectors, contracts/completions/docs/full.json refresh."
  "2026-06-10T10:46:38.613Z",codex-impl,"Evidence: implemented linked-test --add-json for complex command metadata, pm test --run selectors (--match/--only-index/--only-last) with selection metadata and background arg preservation, and aggregate --completion progress counters. Focused gates passed: tsc --noEmit; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/linked-test-parsers.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/runtime-schema-command-flags.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/aggregate-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts; pnpm contracts:check. PM-owned linked tests passed after setting the contracts gate to tracker context. Manual temp-dir smoke passed for init/create/test --add-json/test --run --match/aggregate --completion with isolated PM_PATH and PM_GLOBAL_PATH. Wider gates passed: node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (149 files, 2645 tests), pnpm quality:static, pnpm security:scan, pnpm audit --audit-level low, pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10, pm health --check-only --summary --json, pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift (history drift ok; pre-existing resolution metadata warnings remain)."
  "2026-06-10T10:59:37.752Z",codex-impl,"Review response evidence: addressed Gemini review findings by using Object.hasOwn for --add-json key reads, rejecting empty numeric strings, requiring positive integer timeout_seconds, requiring --match/--only-index/--only-last to be paired with --run, and normalizing aggregate completion statuses against the runtime registry. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/linked-test-parsers.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/aggregate-command.spec.ts (92 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check && pnpm contracts:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10; pnpm security:scan."
  "2026-06-10T11:08:46.556Z",codex-impl,"Review response evidence: addressed follow-up Gemini/CodeRabbit findings by preserving numeric onlyIndex values in command wiring, exposing pm test --list in bash/zsh/fish completions, exposing aggregate --completion in zsh completion, adding aggregate completion other counts for non-open/non-active/non-done statuses, and adding the aggregate completion action schema property. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/aggregate-command.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/unit/runtime-schema-command-flags.spec.ts tests/unit/test-command.spec.ts tests/unit/linked-test-parsers.spec.ts (208 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm changelog:pm:check && pnpm contracts:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10; pnpm security:scan."
  "2026-06-10T12:05:06.662Z",codex-read-surface-20260610,"Read-surface sub-agent finding: pm-awfr and pm-eaer are implemented on main; remaining pm-ojpq gap is context focus/recent sections: add children_total/children_closed/completion_pct to high_level focus items and add recently_created/unparented context sections plus section enums/settings/renderers/contracts/tests."
  "2026-06-10T12:05:14.842Z",codex-mutation-surface-20260610,"Mutation-surface sub-agent finding: remaining gaps persist on current main. pm-xnkd needs close --duplicate-of wiring/validation/metadata/canonical comment; pm-p9hw needs create --parent fail-fast default plus explicit allow-missing-parent escape hatch; pm-esf6 needs root/MCP id-only projection. Change src/cli/commands/{close,create}.ts, src/cli/register-mutation.ts, src/core/{item/parent-reference-policy,output/mutation-projection,shared/command-types}.ts, src/core/output/output.ts, src/cli/{main,registration-helpers}.ts, src/mcp/server.ts, src/sdk/cli-contracts*.ts, src/cli/commands/completion.ts, tests/unit/{close-command,create-command,mutation-projection,output,registration-helpers,completion-command,contracts-command}.spec.ts, tests/integration/{cli,mcp-handshake,release-readiness-runtime}.spec.ts, tests/fixtures/contracts/full.json, docs/{COMMANDS,AGENT_GUIDE}.md."
  "2026-06-10T12:16:40.525Z",codex-impl,"Evidence: implemented remaining mutation/context surfaces: close --duplicate-of with duplicate_of metadata and auto closure fields, create --parent fail-fast default with --allow-missing-parent escape hatch, global --id-only output, MCP idOnly/duplicateOf controls, and context high-level completion plus recently_created/unparented sections. Focused verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts tests/unit/output.spec.ts tests/unit/completion-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts tests/integration/release-readiness-runtime.spec.ts; pnpm contracts:check."
  "2026-06-10T12:28:33.119Z",codex-impl,"Evidence: completed remaining pm SDK/CLI primitives bundle and tracker plan steps. Manual isolated temp smoke passed for create --json --id-only, strict missing parent rejection, --allow-missing-parent, close --duplicate-of metadata, and context recently_created/unparented sections. Verification passed: npm install -g .; pm --version 2026.6.9; node -v v25.9.0; pnpm -v 10.33.4; pnpm build; pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; focused mutation/context tests; pnpm contracts:check; node scripts/run-tests.mjs coverage (149 files, 2650 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm quality:docs-links; pnpm security:scan; pnpm audit --audit-level low; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10; pm health --check-only --summary --json; pm validate --check-resolution --check-history-drift (history drift ok, pre-existing closed-item resolution warnings remain)."
  "2026-06-10T12:37:31.648Z",codex-impl,"Review response evidence: addressed Gemini feedback on PR #198 by moving duplicate self-validation before item scans, tracking duplicate fallback fields precisely so changed_fields only reports actual mutations, and rendering malformed recently_created timestamps as unknown. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts (58 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10."
  "2026-06-10T12:45:44.982Z",codex-impl,"Review response evidence: addressed follow-up Gemini feedback on PR #198 by guarding recently_created sort against missing legacy timestamps and rejecting circular duplicate references when a duplicate target already points back to the closing item. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts (60 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10."
  "2026-06-10T12:51:38.517Z",codex-impl,"Review response evidence: addressed latest Gemini feedback on PR #198 by detecting duplicate_of cycles through the full target chain and making RecentContextItem.created_at optional to match legacy-safe rendering/sorting. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts (61 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10."
  "2026-06-10T12:56:34.697Z",codex-impl,"Review response evidence: addressed CodeRabbit feedback on PR #198 by rejecting duplicate targets that are themselves duplicates, adding strict-governance allowMissingParent coverage, adding idOnly/fullChangedFields to MCP action schema global keys, and regenerating the contract snapshot with create --allow-missing-parent. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/create-command.spec.ts tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/contracts-command.spec.ts (124 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10."
  "2026-06-10T13:03:00.281Z",codex-impl,"Review response evidence: addressed latest Gemini feedback on PR #198 by forwarding top-level MCP pm_create allowMissingParent into create options, filling duplicate fallback metadata when existing values are blank strings, sorting context timestamps with finite timestamp guards, and treating whitespace-only parent metadata as unparented. Verification passed: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts (82 tests); pnpm contracts:check; pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10."
  "2026-06-10T13:11:08.527Z",codex-impl,"Review response: Applied Gemini memory optimization in close duplicate-chain validation by populating the item lookup Map directly with a for...of loop. Verification: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts (39 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10 unchanged."
  "2026-06-10T13:18:26.127Z",codex-impl,"Review response: Addressed latest Gemini suggestions by reusing a single duplicate target lookup Map in close validation and hoisting MCP close duplicateOf through the shared options normalization path. Verification: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts (57 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10 unchanged."
  "2026-06-10T13:26:59.908Z",codex-impl,"Review response: Addressed latest Gemini opportunities by changing close duplicate validation to locate/read only the requested canonical target and duplicate chain on demand, with a small per-command cache, and by hardening context recently_created timestamp parsing/rendering for compact legacy dates and impossible calendar dates. Verification: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/close-command.spec.ts tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts tests/integration/mcp-dynamic-package-actions.spec.ts (82 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10 unchanged."
  "2026-06-10T13:33:30.104Z",codex-impl,"Review response: Addressed latest Gemini performance note by precomputing recently_created timestamp sort keys before sorting, avoiding repeated timestamp parsing in the comparator. Verification: pnpm exec tsc --noEmit --pretty false; node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/context-command.spec.ts (25 tests); pnpm quality:static; pnpm security:scan; pnpm changelog:pm:check with pm-changelog@2026.6.10 unchanged."
